01:51:51.460 --> 01:51:52.460
It was an accident.

01:51:52.460 --> 01:51:53.460
These things happen, right?

01:51:53.460 --> 01:51:55.460
She didn't just trip.

01:51:55.460 --> 01:51:56.460
It was a dog.

01:51:56.460 --> 01:51:57.460
Where's the dog?

01:51:57.460 --> 01:52:07.200
It was tough, one wish.

01:52:07.200 --> 01:52:09.200
And something evil happen each time

01:52:09.200 --> 01:52:11.200
to make the wishes come true.

01:52:11.200 --> 01:52:13.200
Cool.

01:52:13.200 --> 01:52:17.200
Hey, I'd wish for a million bucks and take my chances.

01:52:17.200 --> 01:52:19.200
So, what happened?

01:52:19.200 --> 01:52:22.200
That night, Dougie's parents went out for dinner.

01:52:22.200 --> 01:52:25.200
So, Kevin came over.

01:52:25.200 --> 01:52:28.200
And he brought something with him.

01:52:28.200 --> 01:52:30.200
The gold medley one in the 600.

01:52:30.200 --> 01:52:32.960
It broke his leg.

01:52:32.960 --> 01:52:34.960
You wished it to happen and it did.

01:52:34.960 --> 01:52:35.960
It was an accident.

01:52:35.960 --> 01:52:37.960
Miss Chloe said to be careful what we wish for

01:52:37.960 --> 01:52:39.960
because we might get it.

01:52:39.960 --> 01:52:41.960
Dougie, get a grip.

01:52:41.960 --> 01:52:43.960
There's nothing magic going on here.

01:52:43.960 --> 01:52:44.960
Yeah?

01:52:44.960 --> 01:52:46.960
What about those guys that tried to beat us up?

01:52:46.960 --> 01:52:47.960
Where'd they come from?

01:52:47.960 --> 01:52:48.960
Oh, geez.

01:52:48.960 --> 01:52:49.960
Grants are here.

01:52:49.960 --> 01:52:50.960
He'd know what to do.

01:52:50.960 --> 01:52:51.960
Dougie, enough.

01:52:51.960 --> 01:52:54.960
What if my parents find out what happened to Miss Chloe?

01:52:54.960 --> 01:52:55.960
So I'll be grounded for life.

01:52:55.960 --> 01:52:58.960
They're not gonna find out it's over.

01:52:58.960 --> 01:53:01.960
I say we take this back to Miss Chloe's and apologize.

01:53:01.960 --> 01:53:03.960
Then I could tell my folks we did the right thing.

01:53:03.960 --> 01:53:04.960
And forget it.

01:53:04.960 --> 01:53:05.960
No one is telling nobody nothing.

01:53:05.960 --> 01:53:06.960
About my folks.

01:53:06.960 --> 01:53:07.960
About my folks.

01:53:07.960 --> 01:53:08.960
About my folks.

01:53:08.960 --> 01:53:10.960
I wish you'd just lose your folks.

01:53:10.960 --> 01:53:16.510
It moved, didn't it?

01:53:16.510 --> 01:53:17.510
No.

01:53:17.510 --> 01:53:18.510
No, it just...

01:53:18.510 --> 01:53:19.510
You made a wish.

01:53:19.510 --> 01:53:20.510
No, I didn't.

01:53:20.510 --> 01:53:21.510
You wish I'd lose my folks.

01:53:21.510 --> 01:53:22.510
Yeah, but...

01:53:22.510 --> 01:53:35.810
Don't answer me.

01:53:35.810 --> 01:53:37.810
Is this Douglas Freeman?

01:53:37.810 --> 01:53:38.810
Yes.

01:53:38.810 --> 01:53:40.810
This is Lieutenant Crothers from the Cooper City Police.

01:53:40.810 --> 01:53:42.810
I have some bad news for you, son.

01:53:42.810 --> 01:53:44.810
Your parents have been in a car accident.

01:53:44.810 --> 01:53:46.810
They've been taken to the hospital and I'm afraid...

01:53:46.810 --> 01:53:47.810
No!

01:53:47.810 --> 01:53:48.810
Who's that?

01:53:48.810 --> 01:53:50.810
Mom and Dad had an accident.

01:53:50.810 --> 01:53:51.810
They're in the hospital.

01:53:51.810 --> 01:53:52.810
It was the wish.

01:53:52.810 --> 01:53:53.810
The wish?

01:53:53.810 --> 01:53:54.810
It was.

01:53:54.810 --> 01:53:58.430
You wished it.

01:53:58.430 --> 01:53:59.430
It seemed to be okay.

01:53:59.430 --> 01:54:00.430
Yeah.

01:54:00.430 --> 01:54:01.430
No!

01:54:01.430 --> 01:54:03.430
Every time we make a wish, something bad happens.

01:54:03.430 --> 01:54:04.430
Then do something!

01:54:04.430 --> 01:54:05.430
I wish Grant's here.

01:54:05.430 --> 01:54:06.430
He don't want to do it.

01:54:06.430 --> 01:54:07.430
Ah!

01:54:07.430 --> 01:54:16.100
Dougie, your grandfather's dead.

01:54:16.100 --> 01:54:17.100
You don't think.

01:54:17.100 --> 01:54:42.740
It's Grant's car.

01:54:42.740 --> 01:54:43.740
It's him.

01:54:43.740 --> 01:54:51.020
No!

01:54:51.020 --> 01:54:52.020
Where is it?

01:54:52.020 --> 01:54:55.260
The wishes are bad!

01:54:55.260 --> 01:55:03.780
He may be a skeleton.

01:55:03.780 --> 01:55:38.920
Please, no.

01:55:38.920 --> 01:55:40.920
I'm gonna make the wish we should have made from the start.

01:55:40.920 --> 01:55:42.920
We're sorry we broke this closed vase

01:55:42.920 --> 01:55:45.920
and we wish it never, ever happened.

01:55:45.920 --> 01:55:56.260
Don't answer it.

01:55:56.260 --> 01:55:57.260
I got her.

01:55:57.260 --> 01:56:34.470
We forgot our keys.

01:56:34.470 --> 01:56:35.470
Again.

01:56:35.470 --> 01:56:37.470
If I didn't take them, they wouldn't get taken.

01:56:37.470 --> 01:56:42.060
Hi, kid.

01:56:42.060 --> 01:56:44.060
So, you guys are okay?

01:56:44.060 --> 01:56:45.060
Nothing happened?

01:56:45.060 --> 01:56:47.060
You only went over to the Morrison's.

01:56:47.060 --> 01:56:48.060
No, apart from that maniac truck driver

01:56:48.060 --> 01:56:49.060
that almost side-swiped us.

01:56:49.060 --> 01:56:51.060
Oh, it wasn't that dramatic.

01:56:51.060 --> 01:56:52.060
Whoa!

01:56:52.060 --> 01:56:53.060
What's this for?

01:56:53.060 --> 01:56:55.060
I'm just glad to see you.

01:56:55.060 --> 01:56:57.060
We're glad to see you, too.

01:56:57.060 --> 01:56:59.060
Hang out, guys.

01:56:59.060 --> 01:57:02.060
I say we raid the fridge for some ice cream.

01:57:02.060 --> 01:57:09.070
The car.

01:57:09.070 --> 01:57:24.730
Wait.

01:57:24.730 --> 01:57:30.540
How'd that happen?

01:57:30.540 --> 01:57:32.540
Check your pockets.

01:57:32.540 --> 01:57:35.520
My metal's gone.

01:57:35.520 --> 01:57:36.520
Where'd it go?

01:57:36.520 --> 01:57:37.520
Boston's got it.

01:57:37.520 --> 01:57:38.520
See, what?

01:57:38.520 --> 01:57:39.520
He's got it.

01:57:39.520 --> 01:57:41.520
He won the race just like he was supposed to

01:57:41.520 --> 01:57:43.520
and there never was a ghost car

01:57:43.520 --> 01:57:45.520
and those tough guys never chased it.

01:57:45.520 --> 01:57:46.520
What do you mean?

01:57:46.520 --> 01:57:48.520
I mean, I finally made the right wish.

01:57:48.520 --> 01:57:50.520
None of it ever happened.

01:57:50.520 --> 01:57:57.480
Are you sure the car was gone?

01:57:57.480 --> 01:58:20.500
What does it say?

01:58:20.500 --> 01:58:23.500
It says trick or treat.

01:58:23.500 --> 01:58:28.100
All they could hear.

01:58:29.100 --> 01:58:33.100
Was the sound of the wind blowing through the trees

01:58:33.100 --> 01:58:38.430
or was it the cackle of a slide?

01:58:38.430 --> 01:58:48.840
The end.

01:58:48.840 --> 01:59:01.540
I declare this meeting of the Midnight Society closed.

01:59:01.540 --> 01:59:06.140
Until next time, pleasant dreams, everyone.

